    public publish(topic: String, payload: Object, callback: Function) source

    发布topic

    Params:

    NameTypeAttributeDescription
    topic String

    需要发布的topic
    payload Object

    topic的消息内容
    callback Function

    topic发布成功时的回调

    Example:

         channel.publish(
         '/demo/publish_topic', 
         { msg: 'hello' }
         ()=>{
             console.log('/demo/publish_topic message sent');
         }
     );

    public ready(conf: Object): Promise source

    启动接口，channel的其他接口必须等到ready之后才可以安全的调用

    Params:

    NameTypeAttributeDescription
    conf Object

    启动配置
    conf.id String

    用户id
    conf.token String

    用户登录态token

    Return:

    Promise

    Example:

     channel
     .ready()
     .then(()=>{
         // safe to call channel methods now
         channel.subscribe('/demo/push', (msg)=>{
             console.log(msg);
         });
     })
     .catch((err)=>{
         // initialization failed

         // handle error here
         console.error(err);
     });

    public request(topic: String, payload: Object, callback: Function) source

    RPC请求，即利用长连通道进行一次请求和响应的动作

    Params:

    NameTypeAttributeDescription
    topic String

    做RPC请求的topic
    payload Object

    topic的消息内容
    callback Function

    RPC的响应报文回调函数

    Example:

         channel.request(
         '/demo/rpc_topic',
         { msg: 'hello' }
         (err, res)=>{
             if(err){
                 console.warn('/demo/rpc_topic message error:', err);
                 return;
             }

             console.log('/demo/rpc_topic response message:', res);
         }
     )

    public subscribe(topic: String, callback: Function) source

    订阅topic

    Params:

    NameTypeAttributeDescription
    topic String

    需要订阅的topic
    callback Function

    topic的响应函数，注意：该函数可能被多次调用

    Example:

         channel.subscribe('/demo/push', (msg)=>{
         console.log('/demo/push message received:', msg);
     });

    public unsubscribe(topic: String, callback: Function) source

    取消订阅

    Params:

    NameTypeAttributeDescription
    topic String

    取消订阅的topic
    callback Function

    订阅时传入的响应函数，注意：必须是同一个函数，否则无法取消订阅

    Example:

         channel.unsubscribe('/demo/push', callback);
